    {
      "parameters": {
        "content": "## Customer Feedback Pipeline and Daily Digest\n\nTwo trigger types in one workflow.\n\nReal-time path (Webhook):\n1. Receives form submissions via POST /webhook/feedback\n2. Adds timestamp and feedback ID\n3. Saves to Google Sheets\n4. Routes by urgency: rating 1-2 goes to alerts, 3-5 to log\n5. Responds 200 OK to the caller\n\nDaily digest path (Schedule):\n1. Runs every day at 9:00 AM\n2. Reads all feedback from Sheets\n3. Filters yesterday's entries and aggregates stats\n4. Posts a summary to Slack\n\nWebhook body: { name, email, rating, message, source }",
        "width": 460,
        "height": 460,
        "color": 4
      },
      "id": "b2c1d002-0001-4000-8000-000000000014",
      "name": "Sticky Note",
      "type": "n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote",
      "typeVersion": 1,
      "position": [100, -100]
    },
    {
      "parameters": {
        "content": "### Daily Digest Logic\n\nFilters feedback to yesterday only, then calculates:\n- Average rating\n- Urgent count (rating 1-2)\n- Positive count (rating 4-5)\n- Breakdown by source\n- Top 3 highlights\n\nIf nothing came in yesterday, sends\nan \"all quiet\" message instead.",
        "width": 280,
        "height": 260,
        "color": 5
      },
